{
  "stem": "24409.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the Russian-speaking part of Czechoslovakia, it's now the Republic of Moldavia-- to get young people from there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we got people from there, and we got people from Slovakia, and a good number of Viennese Betarim too.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the Viennese were-- [INAUDIBLE] I remember-- in the minority.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On young people, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Old people were not ready to take the chance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, the young people were enterprising.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With 16 people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing was prepared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went-- they went by train to Athens.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in Athens there were these smugglers, prepared a little ship, which brought them as close to the coast as possible, so that they could swim there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were-- it was a flat ship, flat boat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so they swam and waded to the land.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there, they were soon taken up by the people-- by Jewish inhabitants of what was Palestine, which was, for us, always [INAUDIBLE], the Land of Israel.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The landing part was all [INAUDIBLE], job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to organize the part in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if I say I, I have to stress that it's not I.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was a committee of people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was a member of a small group, which was called [INAUDIBLE], which means in English, in spite of everything, we will bring them to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the leader of this group was a journalist with the name of Paul Haller, H-A-L-L-E-R-- politically, a genius.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm sorry that he didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He went to Israel, but he died very early, there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was the main, driving force in it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was not-- I was one of three or four, until '40s, we were very few.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was very active.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I was not the leader of the group.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
